  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0d85\u0dbb\u0dca\u0db6\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dba \u0dc4\u0dda\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0db0\u0db4\u0dd4\u0dbb \u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dda \u0d9a\u0da7\u0dba\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Anuradhapura Hospital's operations are disrupted due to the fuel crisis",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Government Medical Officers' Association says that today (18th) the Anuradhapura Teaching Hospital, other than emergency treatment services, has stopped due to the inability of hospital staff including doctors to report to work due to the ongoing fuel crisis.",
        "The union says that the health workers are in a lot of trouble due to not getting fuel for more than a week to the fuel stations designated only for getting fuel for the health workers.",
        "Dr. Ajantha Rajakaruna, Anuradhapura District Coordinator of the Government Medical Officers' Association, said:",
        "Although the government designated filling stations for health workers and implemented a system of providing fuel only to the health workers, the fuel supply program has failed due to conflicting situations caused by mob groups and local residents near the fuel stations.",
        "As a result, all the health workers including doctors are facing difficulties.",
        "As of today, about ninety percent of the doctors in the Anuradhapura Teaching Hospital are unable to report for duty. Due to this, the patients are also in a lot of trouble.",
        "The patients said that they were uncomfortable due to the shortage of doctors and employees in the hospital. He said that he had paid a lot of money for the taxis due to transportation difficulties and that he had arrived at the hospital a day earlier to attend the clinics due to the absence of buses."
      ],
